DIY BUDDY
Version 1.0

Created with the Corona SDK by Ansca Mobile, http://anscamobile.com

Instructions:

* Download Corona SDK, http://anscamobile.com/corona/
* Open in Corona Simulator to preview on the desktop
* In the Corona Simulator, choose File > Open for Build... to create an app to install on your device
* Main app code is in main.lua.  
* Helper code for button events in ui.lua
